import React from 'react'; import PropTypes from 'prop-types' const Appointment = ({ key, appointment, deleteAppointment }) => (
{appointment.pet}

Date: {appointment.date}

Time: {appointment.time}

Owner Name: {appointment.owner}

Symptoms: {appointment.symptoms}

) Appointment.propTypes={ key: PropTypes.string.isRequired, appointment: PropTypes.object.isRequired, deleteAppointment: PropTypes.func.isRequired, } export default Appointment;
